Use async/await for non-blocking operations throughout the application
- Implement proper error handling and logging using .NET Core's built-in features
- Use dependency injection for better testability and modularity
- Implement authentication and authorization using ASP.NET Identity or JWT tokens
- Use HTTPS for all web communications and implement appropriate CORS policies
- Create API documentation using Swagger/OpenAPI for better API discoverability
- Use Entity Framework Core for database operations and migrations
- Implement proper input validation using FluentValidation or DataAnnotations